Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:40.13,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱 心靈的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:46.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情燃燒 創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:51.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:58.09,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相發誓過的 遙遠的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:04.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的幻想 只有夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:10.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也奪不走 因為是心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:16.31,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 少年都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:20.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 明天的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:27.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 就像天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:35.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 現在就展開羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.78,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当邪恶在此世蔓延之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会现身的希望之战士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身着星座之圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发蕴藏在身体中的能量“小宇宙”进行着战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正是 保护大地上爱与和平的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士光牙寻找雅典娜的旅程还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一行人穿过大溪谷时 遇到了名为罗喜的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是圣衣修复师贵鬼的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗喜为师父寻找传说中的矿石银星砂而来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却遭到了白银圣斗士地狱犬座多莱的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅试图保护罗喜的行动激发了光牙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退了多莱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗喜同光牙等人告别之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了新希望的贵鬼出现在她的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年们 燃起内心的小宇宙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇之火！苍摩、因缘之战！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有两个核心被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再将此事交给旁人处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不说出来我也知道好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了 忍着点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩你刚才就一直在说马上马上的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候能到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你们说饿了饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才特意在去火之遗迹前绕路过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们搞清楚状况没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说马上就到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭！饭！饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等！等！等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可没那些闲钱去那种饭店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要去哪才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 让你一分不花 好东西吃到饱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得越走越凶险了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大哥你回来倒是先跟我们说一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 忙得手忙脚乱的就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了 所谓墨西哥煎玉米卷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这样自己调味吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调味酱和辣椒都很辣 吃的时候要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 苍摩 听说你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然回来了 就得用这道菜给你接风才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍～摩～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得要和我约会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那可是我的台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你们冷静一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是久别重逢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起玩个痛快吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…已经吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 苍摩以前是做什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混混？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良少年？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是黑社会？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 大家都一副很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他人缘好这点我也承认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩他肯定以前就是那副样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 我终于找到你的仇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身盔甲绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证 一定要为老爸你报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想 这大半夜的你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是给父亲扫墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天白天太忙乱了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字星座（Southern Cross）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字星座是所有星座之中最小的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但老爸却逢人就很骄傲地提这事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说 不管是哪方面 拿到第一就是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸是这座城市的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他受到大家的爱戴 也爱着这座城市中的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看着父亲的背影长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬着老爸 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并决心成为圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次将这个想法告诉老爸的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 圣斗士必须十分强大才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你知道要怎么变强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:08:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 那老爸就把变强的最大诀窍传授给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只说一次 你要听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强的诀窍全部都蕴藏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要变强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉我 对于圣斗士而言最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是力量也不是技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍视之物越多 应守护之物越多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变得越来越强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得老爸想传达给我的就是这个道理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有个好父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天还要早起上路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是第三遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火山地区啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名副其实的火之遗迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 铆足干劲出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快感觉到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火属性圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人去太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用问 追上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此路不通的话 另寻别的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵火焰的我 会被火焰击倒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为让你带上点不利条件会刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这种程度无法结束你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 快给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为什么我要把你一人引出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为此处是火之遗迹 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好考虑下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以操纵火的圣斗士 只有你一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需打倒你 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放水晶便会成为天方夜谭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经落入陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子叫你快点滚出来呢！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时刻终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在期待这个时刻的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 一介青铜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为你能轻松地死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是苍摩的小宇宙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小宇宙还真是不同凡响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 小宇宙受感情影响太大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别得意忘形！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄蜂毒针
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这种程度的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以逾越我的愤怒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒 这就是支配你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字星座…可别说你已经忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死白银圣斗士 南十字星座的一摩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死我老爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字星座 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是这个缘由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就让我利用你这股愤怒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字星座 我记得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为 他是我击倒的第一个圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他的儿子竟然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来告诉你 他死前最后的话语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他当时爬在我脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边哭边毫无尊严地叫我饶他一命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你父亲的最后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对饶不了你！！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被愤怒支配了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 清醒一下啊 苍摩！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被愤怒支配了一切了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就让你领略最大的屈辱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你这样沉浸于愤怒 不断燃烧小宇宙的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是白银圣斗士 也无法很好施展招式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁你正要发出奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确信自己即将得胜的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就抓住你露出的破绽 一击结束你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也走不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 苍摩他会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是没有路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚下没路的话 自己开路就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩就在这前面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说他借助了遗迹的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但竟然能发挥出与我对等的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 别被愤怒冲昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 现在和这小子说什么 他都听不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想 苍摩 什么才是强大的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸这里有的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的这里现在又有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸的心里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 愤怒消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮炽焰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦 多亏了大家 我才能在最后关头控制住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就那么战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会中了那女人的圈套 落得事态无法挽回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去追那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和她战斗过后我明白了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我和她还没做出了断 就无法继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰从五老峰前往水之遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲紫龙虽静默而坐 但体内仍保存着强大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念同伴 并独自与白银圣斗士战斗的龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰与紫龙的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛翱翔天际的升龙一般奋起沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五老峰的秘密！继承吧、父亲紫龙的斗志！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经感受到小宇宙的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:08.29,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在五老峰出现了因缘之白银圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:08.29,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的圣斗士、紫龙的小宇宙 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,